            "RawText": "@code\n * IIterator* it = ...;\n *\n * while (it->moveNext() != OPENDAQ_NO_MORE_ITEMS)\n * {\n *      IBaseObject* obj;\n *      it->getCurrent(&obj);\n *      // do something with obj\n * }\n  @endcode",
